Blood Bond	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeature.SpiderServantClassFeatures.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The spider servant gains a +2 bonus on all attack rolls, checks, and saves if it witnesses the drow judicator threatened or harmed. This bonus lasts as long as the threat is immediate and apparent.	KEY:Spider Servant ~ Blood Bond																											SOURCEPAGE:Und

